  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nI'd like to be able to pass a path to a `solc` binary on my machine and have that be used to build the project.\r\nA new flag `--use` could be added to the `BuildArgs` to enable this.\r\n\r\n`dapp` supports this feature, see: https://github.com/dapphub/dapptools/tree/master/src/dapp#solc-version\r\n\r\nThe usecase is to use a locally modified `solc` to build a project\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\nNote that this can be achieved now with `SOLC_PATH`, see:\r\nhttps://github.com/gakonst/ethers-rs/blob/46d7afd65bdcde4171d778523a0eab1ed2ad27e7/ethers-solc/src/compile/mod.rs#L123",
